               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Series II. Other Material contains correspondence, photographs, and a scrapbook documenting Powel's work and theater generally. Correspondence consists of letters to Powel and comments regarding productions of his plays. Photographs consist of stage shots of Yale productions and cartes de visites of actors. The scrapbook contains clippings, printed ephemera, such as theater programs, and photographs.</p>
